s/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:47:49.000Z","msg":"隨時搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94c7659fe3ed63d2200d834d4fa6eba4c9d62b8","tid":748231,"uid":112927,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"單靠認人其實都有機會認錯，仲要成17個<br />\n如果其中一個係無辜嘅，又無律師幫佢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係有做過嘅就吊死班禽獸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27530efcaecd4038774ca5982f9efc7c7b7351c4","tid":748231,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b5f0c341596adc5f151696f3637061931e21d2","tid":748231,"uid":174418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"印度男人係痴撚線 無道德 <br />\n<br />\n恆河水 愈飲愈痴線"},{"pid":"deb19b88cdbe496e40beb37ed6b25b04033ea1e0","tid":748231,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"印度呢啲新聞<br />\n日日都聽到慣哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ac5973228a768b327599946a167ecfe528842c","tid":748231,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"雖然用私刑，但叉叉律師都仲有啲血性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n腥港啲律師就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似十一哥、律師會會長個啲，唔幫香港不特止，仲爭住賣港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}